snippet.title: Bassmaster® Fishing 2022 - 10 Playable Pro Anglers - Trailer
snippet.description:
This Fall, for the first time ever, you’ll be able to play as, or compete against, 10 Elite Series pros in Bassmaster® Fishing 2022! Our artists have worked closely with the anglers to bring them to life in Bassmaster® Fishing 2022. Not only can you play as the pros, but you can kit yourself out with a selection of their real-life sponsors so you can truly immerse yourself in the world of Bassmaster.

Find out more about the 10 Elite Series anglers:
https://bit.ly/BM22-The-Official-Pro-Angler-Team4

Find out more about Bassmaster Fishing 2022 here: 
http://bit.ly/BassmasterFishing22d 

Also, don't forget to sign up for the newsletter: 
http://bit.ly/Bassmaster22Register4

Follow us on our Social Channels:

Facebook: https://bit.ly/3upg6WA 
Twitter: https://bit.ly/3rTZmVP 
Instagram: https://bit.ly/3mpQyGb
